# JavaScript Algorithms and Data Structures Certification (freeCodeCamp)

## 📖 About the Course

The **JavaScript Algorithms and Data Structures Certification** by freeCodeCamp is a comprehensive course designed to build a strong foundation in modern JavaScript programming. The course covers everything from basic syntax to advanced concepts such as object-oriented programming, functional programming, asynchronous JavaScript, and algorithmic problem-solving.

Throughout this course, I am learning how to write clean, efficient, and reusable JavaScript code while developing problem-solving skills that are essential for modern web development.

---

## 🎯 Course Objectives

* Understand JavaScript fundamentals and core programming concepts.
* Learn how to work with arrays, objects, functions, and loops.
* Develop problem-solving and algorithmic thinking skills.
* Master modern JavaScript features such as ES6 syntax and modules.
* Learn Object-Oriented Programming (OOP) and Functional Programming (FP).
* Understand asynchronous programming concepts including Promises and Async/Await.
* Build projects that demonstrate real-world JavaScript applications.

---

## 📚 Topics Covered

### JavaScript Fundamentals

* Variables and Data Types
* Operators and Expressions
* Conditional Statements
* Loops and Iteration
* Functions and Scope

### ES6 and Modern JavaScript

* Arrow Functions
* Template Literals
* Destructuring
* Spread and Rest Operators
* Modules and Imports/Exports

### Data Structures

* Arrays
* Objects
* Sets
* Maps

### Object-Oriented Programming (OOP)

* Classes and Objects
* Constructors
* Inheritance
* Encapsulation
* Polymorphism

### Functional Programming

* Higher-Order Functions
* Pure Functions
* Callbacks
* Array Methods (`map`, `filter`, `reduce`)

### Asynchronous JavaScript

* Promises
* Async/Await
* Fetch API
* Working with APIs

### Browser Storage and Web APIs

* Cookies
* localStorage
* Session Storage
* IndexedDB
* Cache API

### Algorithms and Problem Solving

* Searching Algorithms
* Sorting Algorithms
* Recursion
* Dynamic Programming Basics
* Time and Space Complexity

---

## 🛠️ Skills Gained

* JavaScript Programming
* Problem Solving
* Algorithm Design
* Data Structures
* Debugging
* DOM Manipulation
* Asynchronous Programming
* Clean Code Practices
* Web API Integration

